{"tid":1533151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你想死？入嚟捱我13巴先！","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:24:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T16:24:45.000Z","uid":98813,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3f03de2299711a9b31c28359a2fe60ebdb2f6109","tid":1533151,"uid":98813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:24:45.000Z","msg":"69到而家，就嚟3個月喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢3個月嚟，你見盡100萬人、200萬人、170萬人，仲有好多好多嘅同路人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢老唔撐你？屋企人都唔撐你？你覺得無人撐你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你夠薑同我喺條街度大叫「光復香港」！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下有幾多回應！仲敢話無人撐你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係，人總會一死，但我同你講，你唔可以就咁死！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有手足比人拉，佢哋為乜嘢？為咗香港人、為咗你呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你死咗，咁佢用自己光陰爭取嘅，仲有咩用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解你唔同佢一齊爭取、一齊打呢場仗、一齊贏？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲記唔記得呀？我哋仲要喺煲底除曬gear相認架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你同我記住！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有咩嘢想傾想講，即管上嚟連登講，你唔好同我自己收收埋埋、諗埋一邊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}